Δείκτες τιμών Κατοικιών - Residential Property Price Indices

Source: https://www.centralbank.cy/el/publications/residential-property-price-indices

Common columns for all files:
Year 
The year which the index is valid for

Quarter 
The quarter which the index is valid for.
Valid values:
1 = First quarter (January - March)
2 = Second quarter (April - June)
3 = Third quarter (July - September)
4 = Fourth quarter (October - December)

 
General_Residential_Property_Price_Index.csv 
This file provides the general residential property price index.

General Residential Property Price Index:
The value of general residential property price index.


Residential_Property_Price_Index_By_Type.csv
This file provides the residential property price index by type.

Appartment:
The value of residential property price index for appartments.

House:
The value of residential property price index for houses.


Residential_Property_Price_Index_By_Province.csv
This file provides the residential property price index by province.

Nicosia:
The value of residential property price index for Nicosia.

Limassol:
The value of residential property price index for Limassol.

Larnaca:
The value of residential property price index for Larnaca.

Paphos:
The value of residential property price index for Paphos.

Famagusta:
The value of residential property price index for Famagusta.


Residential_Property_Price_Index_By_Province_Appartments.csv
This file provides the residential property price index for appartments by province.


Residential_Property_Price_Index_By_Province_Houses.csv
This file provides the residential property price index for houses by province.
